   <concept id="FAR_13_305_2" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">13.305-2</ph> Agency responsibilities.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Each agency using imprest funds and third party drafts shall-</p>
         <ol id="d762e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Periodically review and determine whether there is a continuing need for each fund or third party draft account established, and that amounts of those funds or accounts are not in excess of actual needs;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Take prompt action to have imprest funds or third party draft accounts adjusted to a level commensurate with demonstrated needs whenever circumstances warrant such action; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e22">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Develop and issue appropriate implementing regulations. These regulations shall include (but are not limited to) procedures covering-</p>
               <ol id="d762e44" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e28">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                Designation of personnel authorized to make purchases using imprest funds or third party drafts; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e33">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                Documentation of purchases using imprest funds or third party drafts, including documentation of-</p>
                     <ol id="d762e63" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e39">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
										                    Receipt and acceptance of supplies and services by the Government;</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e44">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
										                    Receipt of cash or third party draft payments by the suppliers; and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d789e49">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
										                    Cash advances and reimbursements.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
